<eesti>V&auml;etiseseaduse (RT I 1997, 93, 1563) &sect; 4 t&auml;iendatakse l&otilde;igetega 5 ja 6 j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>Subsections (5) and (6) are added to &sect; 4 of the Fertilizers Act (RT I 1997, 93, 1563) worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(5) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud kohustuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise korral teeb registripidaja tootjale, t&ouml;&ouml;tlejale v&otilde;i importijale ettekirjutuse andmete esitamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>"(5) Upon failure by a manufacturer, processor or importer to perform the obligation provided for in subsection (2) of this section, the registrar shall issue the manufacturer, processor or importer a precept for the submission of data. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettekirjutuse mittet&auml;itmisel v&otilde;ib registripidaja rakendada sunniraha asendust&auml;itmise ja sunniraha seaduses s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>Upon failure by a manufacturer, processor or importer to comply with the precept, the registrar may impose penalty payment pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Substitutive Enforcement and Penalty Payment Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 5 nimetatud sunniraha &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r on 10 000 krooni." </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The upper limit of penalty payment specified in subsection (5) of this section is 10 000 kroons." </inglise>
